text: Greeeen, or GReeeeN, or The Green is a Japanese J-pop group. The group released their first album in 2007. Two of their most successful songs are "Ai uta" and "Kiseki". GReeeeN is a group of four singers: Hide, Navi, Soh, and 92. Category:J-pop music groups Category:Japanese pop music groups
title: Greeeen
